OuterRecoveryWithInnerThrow
/ Outer recovery body — throws again with its own on-error to capture the inner error message. Used by InnerErrorVarShadowsOuter and OuterErrorVarVisibleAfterInnerHandlerCloses.
- throw error "inner-boom", on error set %innerSeen% = %!error.Message%
- set %outerSeenAfterInner% = %!error.Message%
